<s> Yes, by default Amaya displays p, h1, h2 as blocks.  </s>
<s> Amaya 6.0 and the future Amaya 6.1 make some progresses in the implementation of CSS but they don't provide a full support of CSS2.  </s>
<s> This selector is still not interpreted by Amaya.  </s>
<s> This is due to a lack of manpower, so if you want to contribute that can help us.  </s>
